<div class="container px-0" data-controller="update-form">
<legend class="style-legend">
  <span class="greyed-in">Pick a style </span></a>
  <span class="greyed-inactive">> Pick a room</span></a>
  <span class="greyed-inactive">> Pick a design</span></a>
  <span class="greyed-inactive">> Payment</span>
</legend>

<h2 class="pt-4">Pick your style</h2>
  <form
    id="styles-form"
    action="/presets"
    method="GET"
    data-update-form-target="form"
  >
    <fieldset class ="fieldset-1">
        <div class="radio-container">


          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card1">
              <input type="radio" id="card1" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Modern">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Modern_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Modern</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Modern style features clean lines, simple forms, and neutral colors. It often incorporates materials like glass, metal, and concrete</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card2">
              <input type="radio" id="card2" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Minimalistic">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Minimalistic_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Minimalistic</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Minimalistic design is characterized by a focus on function and simplicity. This style emphasizes clean, uncluttered spaces, and a limited color palette.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card3">
              <input type="radio" id="card3" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Scandinavian">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Scandinavian_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Scandinavian</h2>
                <p class="style-description">This style is known for its simplicity, functionality, and use of natural materials. Scandinavian design often features a light color palette, clean lines, and cozy textures.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card4">
              <input type="radio" id="card4" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Industrial">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Industrial_Style.webp", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Industrial</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Industrial design is characterized by exposed brick walls, metal piping, and raw materials. It often features a color palette of neutral tones and raw, unfinished textures.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card5">
              <input type="radio" id="card5" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Bohemian">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Bohemian_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Bohemian</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Bohemian style is all about a free-spirited, eclectic mix of colors, patterns, and textures. It often incorporates elements from different cultures and eras.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card6">
              <input type="radio" id="card6" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Coastal">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Coastal_Style.webp", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Coastal</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Coastal design is inspired by the ocean and the beach. It often features light, airy colors and natural materials like wood and wicker.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card7">
              <input type="radio" id="card7" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Traditional">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Traditional_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Traditional</h2>
                <p class="style-description">This style is characterized by classic, timeless designs, and a focus on elegance and sophistication. Traditional interiors often feature ornate furniture and textiles, and a muted color palette.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card8">
              <input type="radio" id="card8" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Mid-century">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Mid-century modern_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Mid-century</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Mid-century modern design emerged in the mid-20th century and is characterized by a focus on simplicity, function, and clean lines. It often features bold pops of color and a mix of materials like wood, metal, and glass.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card9">
              <input type="radio" id="card9" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Art deco">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Art_deco_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Art deco</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Art deco design is inspired by the glamour and opulence of the 1920s and 1930s. It features bold geometric shapes, luxurious materials, and a strong emphasis on symmetry.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card10">
              <input type="radio" id="card10" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Rustic">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Rustic_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Rustic</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Rustic design is all about embracing natural materials and textures like wood, stone, and metal. It often features warm, earthy colors and a cozy, inviting feel.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card11">
              <input type="radio" id="card11" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Shabby chic">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Shabby_Chic_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Shabby chic</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Shabby chic design is characterized by a vintage, worn-in look. It often features distressed furniture and soft, muted colors.</p>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="style-card" data-action="click->update-form#scroll">
              <label for="card12">
              <input type="radio" id="card12" name="style" class="hide-checkbox" value="Urban">
                <%= image_tag "Favorite_Style/Urban_Style.jpg", class: "style-img" %>
                <h2 class="style-title">Urban</h2>
                <p class="style-description">Urban style in interior design is raw and industrial, mixing vintage and contemporary elements with neutral colors and bold accents.</p>
              </label>
          </div>
        </div>




    </fieldset>

    <legend class="style-legend proper-scroll-padding">
      <a href="#"><span class="greyed-out">Pick a style ></span></a>
      <span class="greyed-in">  Pick a room ></span></a>
      <span class="greyed-inactive"> Pick a design ></span></a>
      <span class="greyed-inactive"> Payment</span>

    </legend>

    <h2 class="pt-4">Pick a room to design</h2>

    <fieldset class="room-type" data-update-form-target="rooms" id="rooms">

      <div class="radio-container2">

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room1">
              <input type="radio" id="room1" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Living room">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_LivingRooms.jpg", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Living room</h2>
                <p class="room-description">A living room is used for entertaining friends, talking, reading, or watching television.</p>
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room2">
              <input type="radio" id="room2" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Kitchen">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_Kitchen.jpg", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Kitchen</h2>
                <p class="room-description">The kitchen used for cooking and food preparation in a dwelling.</p>
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room3">
              <input type="radio" id="room3" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Bathroom">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_Bathrooms.jpg", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Bathroom</h2>
                <p class="room-description">A bathroom is a room that contains a bath or shower, a washbasin, and toilet.</p>
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room4">
              <input type="radio" id="room4" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Bedroom">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_BedRoom.jpg", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Bedroom</h2>
                <p class="room-description">A bedroom is used for sleeping and rest.</p>
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room5">
              <input type="radio" id="room5" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Office">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_office s.jpg", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Office</h2>
                <p class="room-description">A office room is used for business and communication.</p>
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="room-card" data-action="click->update-form#submit">
            <label for="room6">
              <input type="radio" id="room6" name="room" class="hide-checkbox" value="Nook">
                <%= image_tag "Modern_Rooms/Modern_Nook.webp", class: "room-img" %>
                <h2 class="room-title">Nook</h2>
                <p class="room-description">Sheltered and secluded place and a place for privacy, peace and quiet.</p>
            </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </fieldset>
  </form>
</div>
